<A NAME="eolPage77"></A>
<P STYLE="TEXT-ALIGN:CENTER;MARGIN-BOTTOM:12PT;MARGIN-TOP:0PT;TEXT-INDENT:0%;FONT-WEIGHT:BOLD;TEXT-TRANSFORM:UPPERCASE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN;FONT-STYLE:NORMAL;FONT-VARIANT: NORMAL;">
<A NAME="MCZ-EX1028_414_HTM__AEIOULASTRENDEREDPAGEBREAKAEIOU3">
</A>
<FONT STYLE="TEXT-DECORATION:NONE;">
	Article III
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="TEXT-DECORATION:UNDERLINE;FONT-WEIGHT:NORMAL;TEXT-TRANSFORM:NONE;">
<BR>
	Conditions of Effectiveness
</FONT>
</P>
<P STYLE="TEXT-ALIGN:JUSTIFY;MARGIN-BOTTOM:12PT;MARGIN-TOP:0PT;TEXT-INDENT:7.69%;FONT-SIZE:12PT;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN;FONT-WEIGHT:NORMAL;FONT-STYLE:NORMAL;TEXT-TRANSFORM:NONE;FONT-VARIANT: NORMAL;">
<FONT STYLE="TEXT-DECORATION:UNDERLINE;">
	Effective Time
</FONT>
</P>
<P STYLE="TEXT-ALIGN:JUSTIFY;MARGIN-BOTTOM:12PT;MARGIN-TOP:0PT;TEXT-INDENT:7.69%;FONT-SIZE:12PT;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN;FONT-WEIGHT:NORMAL;FONT-STYLE:NORMAL;TEXT-TRANSFORM:NONE;FONT-VARIANT: NORMAL;">
	.&nbsp;&nbsp;This Amendment is effective as of the date first written above once the following conditions precedent have been satisfied in full (the &#8220;
<FONT STYLE="TEXT-DECORATION:UNDERLINE;">
	Effective Time
</FONT>
	&#8221;):
</P>
<P STYLE="TEXT-ALIGN:JUSTIFY;MARGIN-BOTTOM:12PT;MARGIN-TOP:0PT;TEXT-INDENT:7.69%;FONT-SIZE:12PT;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN;FONT-WEIGHT:NORMAL;FONT-STYLE:NORMAL;TEXT-TRANSFORM:NONE;FONT-VARIANT: NORMAL;">
	(a)
<FONT STYLE="MARGIN-LEFT:72PT;">
</FONT>
	Administrative Agent shall have received, at Administrative Agent&#8217;s office, a duly executed counterpart of this Amendment from each Credit Party;
</P>
<P STYLE="TEXT-ALIGN:JUSTIFY;MARGIN-BOTTOM:12PT;MARGIN-TOP:0PT;TEXT-INDENT:7.69%;FONT-SIZE:12PT;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN;FONT-WEIGHT:NORMAL;FONT-STYLE:NORMAL;TEXT-TRANSFORM:NONE;FONT-VARIANT: NORMAL;">
	(b)
<FONT STYLE="MARGIN-LEFT:72PT;">
</FONT>
	Administrative Agent shall have received, in immediately available funds, an amendment fee equal to $25,000; and
</P>
<P STYLE="TEXT-ALIGN:JUSTIFY;MARGIN-BOTTOM:12PT;MARGIN-TOP:0PT;TEXT-INDENT:7.69%;FONT-SIZE:12PT;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN;FONT-WEIGHT:NORMAL;FONT-STYLE:NORMAL;TEXT-TRANSFORM:NONE;FONT-VARIANT: NORMAL;">
	(c)
<FONT STYLE="MARGIN-LEFT:72PT;">
</FONT>
	No Default or Event of Default shall have occurred and be continuing.
</P>
<P STYLE="TEXT-ALIGN:CENTER;MARGIN-BOTTOM:12PT;MARGIN-TOP:0PT;TEXT-INDENT:0%;FONT-WEIGHT:BOLD;TEXT-TRANSFORM:UPPERCASE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN;FONT-STYLE:NORMAL;FONT-VARIANT: NORMAL;">
<FONT STYLE="TEXT-DECORATION:NONE;">
	Article IV
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="TEXT-DECORATION:UNDERLINE;FONT-WEIGHT:NORMAL;TEXT-TRANSFORM:NONE;">
<BR>
	Representations and Warranties
</FONT>
</P>
<P STYLE="TEXT-ALIGN:JUSTIFY;MARGIN-BOTTOM:12PT;MARGIN-TOP:0PT;TEXT-INDENT:7.69%;FONT-SIZE:12PT;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN;FONT-WEIGHT:NORMAL;FONT-STYLE:NORMAL;TEXT-TRANSFORM:NONE;FONT-VARIANT: NORMAL;">
<FONT STYLE="TEXT-DECORATION:UNDERLINE;">
	Representations and Warranties of Credit Parties
</FONT>
</P>
<P STYLE="TEXT-ALIGN:JUSTIFY;MARGIN-BOTTOM:12PT;MARGIN-TOP:0PT;TEXT-INDENT:7.69%;FONT-SIZE:12PT;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN;FONT-WEIGHT:NORMAL;FONT-STYLE:NORMAL;TEXT-TRANSFORM:NONE;FONT-VARIANT: NORMAL;">
	.&nbsp;&nbsp;In order to induce Administrative Agent and the Lenders to enter into this Amendment, each Credit Party hereby represents and warrants to Administrative Agent and the Lenders that:
</P>
<P STYLE="TEXT-ALIGN:JUSTIFY;MARGIN-BOTTOM:12PT;MARGIN-TOP:0PT;TEXT-INDENT:7.69%;FONT-SIZE:12PT;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN;FONT-WEIGHT:NORMAL;FONT-STYLE:NORMAL;TEXT-TRANSFORM:NONE;FONT-VARIANT: NORMAL;">
	(a)
<FONT STYLE="MARGIN-LEFT:72PT;">
</FONT>
	The representations and warranties contained in Article VII of the Original Loan Agreement are true and correct in all material respects at and as of the Effective Time;
<FONT STYLE="TEXT-DECORATION:UNDERLINE;">
	provided
</FONT>
	,
<FONT STYLE="TEXT-DECORATION:UNDERLINE;">
	however
</FONT>
	, those representations and warranties containing a reference to a particular date shall continue to be qualified by reference to such date;
</P>
<P STYLE="TEXT-ALIGN:JUSTIFY;MARGIN-BOTTOM:12PT;MARGIN-TOP:0PT;TEXT-INDENT:7.69%;FONT-SIZE:12PT;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN;FONT-WEIGHT:NORMAL;FONT-STYLE:NORMAL;TEXT-TRANSFORM:NONE;FONT-VARIANT: NORMAL;">
	(b)
<FONT STYLE="MARGIN-LEFT:72PT;">
</FONT>
	It is duly authorized to execute and deliver this Amendment and is duly authorized to borrow and perform its obligations under the Loan Agreement and the other Loan Documents.&nbsp;&nbsp;It has duly taken all corporate action necessary to authorize the execution and delivery of this Amendment and to authorize the performance of the obligations of such Credit Party hereunder;
</P>
<P STYLE="TEXT-ALIGN:JUSTIFY;MARGIN-BOTTOM:12PT;MARGIN-TOP:0PT;TEXT-INDENT:7.69%;FONT-SIZE:12PT;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN;FONT-WEIGHT:NORMAL;FONT-STYLE:NORMAL;TEXT-TRANSFORM:NONE;FONT-VARIANT: NORMAL;">
	(c)
<FONT STYLE="MARGIN-LEFT:72PT;">
</FONT>
	The execution and delivery by it of this Amendment, the performance by it of its obligations hereunder and the consummation of the transactions contemplated hereby do not and will not conflict with, violate or constitute a breach or default under (i) any provision of Applicable Law applicable or binding upon it, except where such conflict, violation, breach or default reasonably would not be expected to result in a Material Adverse Effect, (ii) its organizational documents, (iii) any agreement or instrument to which it is a party or which is otherwise binding upon it, or (iv) any material judgment, license, order or permit applicable to or binding upon it;
</P>
<P STYLE="TEXT-ALIGN:JUSTIFY;MARGIN-BOTTOM:12PT;MARGIN-TOP:0PT;TEXT-INDENT:7.69%;FONT-SIZE:12PT;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN;FONT-WEIGHT:NORMAL;FONT-STYLE:NORMAL;TEXT-TRANSFORM:NONE;FONT-VARIANT: NORMAL;">
	(d)
<FONT STYLE="MARGIN-LEFT:72PT;">
</FONT>
	Except for those which have been duly obtained, no consent, approval, exemption, authorization or other action by, notice to, or filing with any Governmental Authority or third party is required in connection with the execution and delivery by such Credit Party of this Amendment or to consummate the transactions contemplated hereby; and
</P>
<P STYLE="TEXT-ALIGN:JUSTIFY;MARGIN-BOTTOM:12PT;MARGIN-TOP:0PT;TEXT-INDENT:7.69%;FONT-SIZE:12PT;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN;FONT-WEIGHT:NORMAL;FONT-STYLE:NORMAL;TEXT-TRANSFORM:NONE;FONT-VARIANT: NORMAL;">
<A NAME="MCZ-EX1028_414_HTM__AEIOULASTRENDEREDPAGEBREAKAEIOU4">
</A>
	(e)
<FONT STYLE="MARGIN-LEFT:72PT;">
</FONT>
	When duly executed and delivered, this Amendment will constitute a legal, valid and binding obligation of each Credit Party, enforceable in accordance with its terms, except as
</P>
<P STYLE="MARGIN-TOP:12PT;MARGIN-BOTTOM:0PT;TEXT-INDENT:0%;FONT-SIZE:8PT;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN;FONT-WEIGHT:NORMAL;FONT-STYLE:NORMAL;TEXT-TRANSFORM:NONE;FONT-VARIANT: NORMAL;">
<FONT STYLE="TEXT-DECORATION:UNDERLINE;">
	SECOND AMENDMENT TO LOAN AND SECURITY AGREEMENT (Mad Catz)
</FONT>
	- Page 3
</P>
<HR STYLE="PAGE-BREAK-AFTER:ALWAYS;WIDTH:100%;">
<A NAME="eolPage78"></A>
<P STYLE="TEXT-ALIGN:JUSTIFY;MARGIN-BOTTOM:12PT;MARGIN-TOP:0PT;FONT-SIZE:12PT;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN;FONT-WEIGHT:NORMAL;FONT-STYLE:NORMAL;TEXT-TRANSFORM:NONE;FONT-VARIANT: NORMAL;">
<FONT STYLE="FONT-SIZE:12PT;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN;FONT-WEIGHT:NORMAL;FONT-STYLE:NORMAL;TEXT-TRANSFORM:NONE;FONT-VARIANT: NORMAL;">
	limited by bankruptcy, insolvency, reorganization, moratorium or
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="FONT-SIZE:12PT;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN;FONT-WEIGHT:NORMAL;FONT-STYLE:NORMAL;TEXT-TRANSFORM:NONE;FONT-VARIANT: NORMAL;">
	similar laws relating to enforcement of creditors&#8217; rights.
</FONT>
</P>
<P STYLE="TEXT-ALIGN:CENTER;MARGIN-BOTTOM:12PT;MARGIN-TOP:0PT;TEXT-INDENT:0%;FONT-WEIGHT:BOLD;TEXT-TRANSFORM:UPPERCASE;FONT-SIZE:12PT;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN;FONT-STYLE:NORMAL;FONT-VARIANT: NORMAL;">
<FONT STYLE="TEXT-DECORATION:NONE;">
	Article V
</FONT>
<FONT STYLE="TEXT-DECORATION:UNDERLINE;FONT-WEIGHT:NORMAL;TEXT-TRANSFORM:NONE;">
<BR>
	Miscellaneous
</FONT>
</P>
<P STYLE="TEXT-ALIGN:JUSTIFY;MARGIN-BOTTOM:12PT;MARGIN-TOP:0PT;TEXT-INDENT:7.69%;FONT-SIZE:12PT;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN;FONT-WEIGHT:NORMAL;FONT-STYLE:NORMAL;TEXT-TRANSFORM:NONE;FONT-VARIANT: NORMAL;">
<FONT STYLE="TEXT-DECORATION:UNDERLINE;">
	Ratification of Agreement
</FONT>
</P>
<P STYLE="TEXT-ALIGN:JUSTIFY;MARGIN-BOTTOM:12PT;MARGIN-TOP:0PT;TEXT-INDENT:7.69%;FONT-SIZE:12PT;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN;FONT-WEIGHT:NORMAL;FONT-STYLE:NORMAL;TEXT-TRANSFORM:NONE;FONT-VARIANT: NORMAL;">
	.&nbsp;&nbsp;The Original Loan Agreement as hereby amended is hereby ratified and confirmed in all respects.&nbsp;&nbsp;Any reference to the Loan Agreement in any Loan Document shall be deemed to refer to the Original Loan Agreement, as amended by this Amendment.&nbsp;&nbsp;The execution, delivery and effectiveness of this Amendment shall not, except as expressly provided herein, operate as a waiver of any right, power or remedy of Administrative Agent or Lenders under the Loan Agreement or any other Loan Document nor constitute a waiver of any provision of the Loan Agreement or any other Loan Document.
</P>
<P STYLE="TEXT-ALIGN:JUSTIFY;MARGIN-BOTTOM:12PT;MARGIN-TOP:0PT;TEXT-INDENT:7.69%;FONT-SIZE:12PT;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN;FONT-WEIGHT:NORMAL;FONT-STYLE:NORMAL;TEXT-TRANSFORM:NONE;FONT-VARIANT: NORMAL;">
<FONT STYLE="TEXT-DECORATION:UNDERLINE;">
	Survival of Agreements
</FONT>
</P>
<P STYLE="TEXT-ALIGN:JUSTIFY;MARGIN-BOTTOM:12PT;MARGIN-TOP:0PT;TEXT-INDENT:7.69%;FONT-SIZE:12PT;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN;FONT-WEIGHT:NORMAL;FONT-STYLE:NORMAL;TEXT-TRANSFORM:NONE;FONT-VARIANT: NORMAL;">
	.&nbsp;&nbsp;All representations, warranties, covenants and agreements of the Credit Parties herein shall survive the execution and delivery of this Amendment and the performance hereof, and shall further survive until all of the Obligations are paid in full.&nbsp;&nbsp;All statements and agreements contained in any certificate or instrument delivered by any Credit Party hereunder or under the Loan Agreement to Administrative Agent shall be deemed to constitute representations and warranties by, or agreements and covenants of, such Credit Party under this Amendment and under the Loan Agreement.
</P>
<P STYLE="TEXT-ALIGN:JUSTIFY;MARGIN-BOTTOM:12PT;MARGIN-TOP:0PT;TEXT-INDENT:7.69%;FONT-SIZE:12PT;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN;FONT-WEIGHT:NORMAL;FONT-STYLE:NORMAL;TEXT-TRANSFORM:NONE;FONT-VARIANT: NORMAL;">
<FONT STYLE="TEXT-DECORATION:UNDERLINE;">
	Loan Document
</FONT>
</P>
<P STYLE="TEXT-ALIGN:JUSTIFY;MARGIN-BOTTOM:12PT;MARGIN-TOP:0PT;TEXT-INDENT:7.69%;FONT-SIZE:12PT;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN;FONT-WEIGHT:NORMAL;FONT-STYLE:NORMAL;TEXT-TRANSFORM:NONE;FONT-VARIANT: NORMAL;">
	.&nbsp;&nbsp;This Amendment is a Loan Document, and all provisions in the Loan Agreement pertaining to Loan Documents apply hereto.
</P>
<P STYLE="TEXT-ALIGN:JUSTIFY;MARGIN-BOTTOM:12PT;MARGIN-TOP:0PT;TEXT-INDENT:7.69%;FONT-SIZE:12PT;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN;FONT-WEIGHT:NORMAL;FONT-STYLE:NORMAL;TEXT-TRANSFORM:NONE;FONT-VARIANT: NORMAL;">
<FONT STYLE="TEXT-DECORATION:UNDERLINE;">
	Governing Law
</FONT>
</P>
<P STYLE="TEXT-ALIGN:JUSTIFY;MARGIN-BOTTOM:12PT;MARGIN-TOP:0PT;TEXT-INDENT:7.69%;FONT-SIZE:12PT;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN;FONT-WEIGHT:NORMAL;FONT-STYLE:NORMAL;TEXT-TRANSFORM:NONE;FONT-VARIANT: NORMAL;">
	.&nbsp;&nbsp;THIS AMENDMENT SHALL BE GOVERNED AND CONSTRUED IN ACCORDANCE WITH THE LAWS OF THE STATE OF TEXAS WITHOUT REGARD TO ITS CONFLICT OF LAW PRINCIPLES.
</P>
<P STYLE="TEXT-ALIGN:JUSTIFY;MARGIN-BOTTOM:12PT;MARGIN-TOP:0PT;TEXT-INDENT:7.69%;FONT-SIZE:12PT;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN;FONT-WEIGHT:NORMAL;FONT-STYLE:NORMAL;TEXT-TRANSFORM:NONE;FONT-VARIANT: NORMAL;">
<FONT STYLE="TEXT-DECORATION:UNDERLINE;">
	Counterparts; Fax
</FONT>
</P>
<P STYLE="TEXT-ALIGN:JUSTIFY;MARGIN-BOTTOM:12PT;MARGIN-TOP:0PT;TEXT-INDENT:7.69%;FONT-SIZE:12PT;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN;FONT-WEIGHT:NORMAL;FONT-STYLE:NORMAL;TEXT-TRANSFORM:NONE;FONT-VARIANT: NORMAL;">
	.&nbsp;&nbsp;This Amendment may be executed in any number of counterparts and signature pages may be detached from multiple separate counterparts and attached to the same document.&nbsp;&nbsp;A telecopy or other electronic transmission of any such executed counterpart signature page shall be deemed valid as an original.
</P>
<P STYLE="TEXT-ALIGN:JUSTIFY;MARGIN-BOTTOM:12PT;MARGIN-TOP:0PT;TEXT-INDENT:7.69%;FONT-WEIGHT:BOLD;FONT-SIZE:12PT;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN;FONT-STYLE:NORMAL;TEXT-TRANSFORM:NONE;FONT-VARIANT: NORMAL;">
	THIS AMENDMENT AND THE OTHER LOAN DOCUMENTS REPRESENT THE FINAL AGREEMENT BETWEEN THE PARTIES AND MAY NOT BE CONTRADICTED BY EVIDENCE OF PRIOR, CONTEMPORANEOUS, OR SUBSEQUENT ORAL AGREEMENTS OF THE PARTIES
<FONT STYLE="FONT-WEIGHT:NORMAL;">
	.
</FONT>
</P>
<P STYLE="TEXT-ALIGN:JUSTIFY;MARGIN-BOTTOM:12PT;MARGIN-TOP:0PT;TEXT-INDENT:7.69%;FONT-WEIGHT:BOLD;FONT-SIZE:12PT;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN;FONT-STYLE:NORMAL;TEXT-TRANSFORM:NONE;FONT-VARIANT: NORMAL;">
	THERE ARE NO UNWRITTEN ORAL AGREEMENTS BETWEEN THE PARTIES
<FONT STYLE="FONT-WEIGHT:NORMAL;">
	.
</FONT>
</P>
<P STYLE="TEXT-ALIGN:CENTER;MARGIN-BOTTOM:0PT;MARGIN-TOP:0PT;TEXT-INDENT:0%;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN;FONT-SIZE:10PT;">
	&nbsp;
</P>
<P STYLE="MARGIN-TOP:12PT;MARGIN-BOTTOM:0PT;TEXT-INDENT:0%;FONT-SIZE:8PT;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN;FONT-WEIGHT:NORMAL;FONT-STYLE:NORMAL;TEXT-TRANSFORM:NONE;FONT-VARIANT: NORMAL;">
<FONT STYLE="TEXT-DECORATION:UNDERLINE;">
	SECOND AMENDMENT TO LOAN AND SECURITY AGREEMENT (Mad Catz)
</FONT>
	- Page 4

	&nbsp;
</P>
<P STYLE="TEXT-ALIGN:JUSTIFY;MARGIN-BOTTOM:12PT;MARGIN-TOP:0PT;TEXT-INDENT:7.69%;FONT-SIZE:12PT;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN;FONT-WEIGHT:NORMAL;FONT-STYLE:NORMAL;TEXT-TRANSFORM:NONE;FONT-VARIANT: NORMAL;">
<A NAME="MCZ-EX1028_414_HTM__AEIOULASTRENDEREDPAGEBREAKAEIOU5">
</A>
<FONT STYLE="FONT-SIZE:12PT;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN;FONT-WEIGHT:NORMAL;FONT-STYLE:NORMAL;TEXT-TRANSFORM:NONE;FONT-VARIANT: NORMAL;">
	IN WITNESS WHEREOF, this Amendment is executed as of the date first above written.
</FONT>

<P STYLE="MARGIN-BOTTOM:0PT;MARGIN-TOP:0PT;MARGIN-LEFT:46.15%;TEXT-INDENT:0%;FONT-WEIGHT:BOLD;COLOR:#000000;FONT-SIZE:11PT;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN;FONT-STYLE:NORMAL;TEXT-TRANSFORM:NONE;FONT-VARIANT: NORMAL;">
<FONT STYLE="TEXT-DECORATION:UNDERLINE;">
	CREDIT PARTIES
</FONT>

	EXHIBIT 23.1

<EFX_EXPERTS_CONSENT>
<A NAME="FIS_EXPERTS_CONSENT"></A>
<P STYLE="TEXT-ALIGN:CENTER;MARGIN-TOP:12PT;MARGIN-BOTTOM:0PT;TEXT-INDENT:0%;FONT-WEIGHT:BOLD;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN;FONT-SIZE:10PT;FONT-STYLE:NORMAL;TEXT-TRANSFORM:NONE;FONT-VARIANT: NORMAL;">
	Consent of Independent Registered Public Accounting Firm
</P>
<P STYLE="MARGIN-TOP:12PT;MARGIN-BOTTOM:0PT;TEXT-INDENT:0%;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN;FONT-SIZE:10PT;FONT-WEIGHT:NORMAL;FONT-STYLE:NORMAL;TEXT-TRANSFORM:NONE;FONT-VARIANT: NORMAL;">
	The Board of Directors
</P>
<P STYLE="MARGIN-BOTTOM:0PT;MARGIN-TOP:0PT;TEXT-INDENT:0%;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN;FONT-SIZE:10PT;FONT-WEIGHT:NORMAL;FONT-STYLE:NORMAL;TEXT-TRANSFORM:NONE;FONT-VARIANT: NORMAL;">
	Mad Catz Interactive, Inc.:
</P>
<P STYLE="MARGIN-TOP:12PT;MARGIN-BOTTOM:0PT;TEXT-INDENT:0%;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN;FONT-SIZE:10PT;FONT-WEIGHT:NORMAL;FONT-STYLE:NORMAL;TEXT-TRANSFORM:NONE;FONT-VARIANT: NORMAL;">
	We consent to incorporation by reference in the registration statements No.&#160;333-103798, No.&#160;333-176813 and No.&#160;333-169947 on Form&#160;S-8 and No.&#160;333-173892 and No. 333-198930&nbsp;&nbsp;on Form S-3 and S-3A of Mad Catz Interactive, Inc. of our report dated June&#160;2, 2016, with respect to the consolidated balance sheets of Mad Catz Interactive, Inc. as of March&#160;31, 2016 and 2015, and the related consolidated statements of operations, comprehensive (loss) income, shareholders&#8217; equity, and cash flows for each of the years in the three-year period ended March&#160;31, 2016, which report appears in the March&#160;31, 2016 Annual Report on Form&#160;10-K of Mad Catz Interactive, Inc.
</P>
<P STYLE="TEXT-ALIGN:JUSTIFY;MARGIN-TOP:12PT;MARGIN-BOTTOM:0PT;TEXT-INDENT:0%;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN;FONT-SIZE:10PT;FONT-WEIGHT:NORMAL;FONT-STYLE:NORMAL;TEXT-TRANSFORM:NONE;FONT-VARIANT: NORMAL;">
	Our report date June 2, 2016 contains an explanatory paragraph that states there are uncertainties about the Company&#8217;s recurring losses from operations and liquidity position, which raises substantial doubt about their ability to continue as a going concern for a reasonable period of time. The consolidated financial statements do not include any adjustments that might result from the outcome of these uncertainties.
</P>
<P STYLE="TEXT-ALIGN:CENTER;MARGIN-TOP:12PT;MARGIN-BOTTOM:0PT;MARGIN-LEFT:68.01%;TEXT-INDENT:-4.86%;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN;FONT-SIZE:10PT;FONT-WEIGHT:NORMAL;FONT-STYLE:NORMAL;TEXT-TRANSFORM:NONE;FONT-VARIANT: NORMAL;">
	/s/ KPMG LLP
</P>
<P STYLE="MARGIN-TOP:12PT;MARGIN-BOTTOM:0PT;TEXT-INDENT:0%;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN;FONT-SIZE:10PT;FONT-WEIGHT:NORMAL;FONT-STYLE:NORMAL;TEXT-TRANSFORM:NONE;FONT-VARIANT: NORMAL;">
	San Diego, California

	June&#160;2, 2016

<P STYLE="MARGIN-TOP:12PT;MARGIN-BOTTOM:0PT;TEXT-INDENT:0%;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN;FONT-SIZE:10PT;FONT-WEIGHT:NORMAL;FONT-STYLE:NORMAL;TEXT-TRANSFORM:NONE;FONT-VARIANT: NORMAL;">

<FONT STYLE="FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN;FONT-SIZE:10PT;FONT-WEIGHT:NORMAL;FONT-STYLE:NORMAL;TEXT-TRANSFORM:NONE;FONT-VARIANT: NORMAL;">
	1.
</FONT>

<A NAME="FIS_CERTIFICATION_3"></A>
<P STYLE="TEXT-ALIGN:CENTER;MARGIN-TOP:12PT;MARGIN-BOTTOM:0PT;TEXT-INDENT:0%;FONT-WEIGHT:BOLD;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN;FONT-SIZE:10PT;FONT-STYLE:NORMAL;TEXT-TRANSFORM:NONE;FONT-VARIANT: NORMAL;">
	Certification of Chief Executive Officer
</P>
<P STYLE="TEXT-ALIGN:CENTER;MARGIN-BOTTOM:0PT;MARGIN-TOP:0PT;TEXT-INDENT:0%;FONT-WEIGHT:BOLD;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN;FONT-SIZE:10PT;FONT-STYLE:NORMAL;TEXT-TRANSFORM:NONE;FONT-VARIANT: NORMAL;">
	Pursuant to Section&#160;906 of the Sarbanes-Oxley Act of 2002
</P>
<P STYLE="MARGIN-TOP:12PT;MARGIN-BOTTOM:0PT;TEXT-INDENT:4.86%;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN;FONT-SIZE:10PT;FONT-WEIGHT:NORMAL;FONT-STYLE:NORMAL;TEXT-TRANSFORM:NONE;FONT-VARIANT: NORMAL;">
	Pursuant to 18 U.S.C. &#167;1350, as created by Section&#160;906 of the Sarbanes-Oxley Act of 2002, the undersigned officer of Mad Catz Interactive, Inc. (the &#8220;
<FONT STYLE="FONT-STYLE:ITALIC;">
	Company
</FONT>
	&#8221;) hereby certifies, to such officer&#8217;s knowledge, that:
</P>
<P STYLE="MARGIN-TOP:6PT;MARGIN-BOTTOM:0PT;TEXT-INDENT:4.86%;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN;FONT-SIZE:10PT;FONT-WEIGHT:NORMAL;FONT-STYLE:NORMAL;TEXT-TRANSFORM:NONE;FONT-VARIANT: NORMAL;">
	(i) the accompanying Annual Report on Form 10-K of the Company for the period ended March&#160;31, 2016 (the &#8220;
<FONT STYLE="FONT-STYLE:ITALIC;">
	Report
</FONT>

</P>
<P STYLE="MARGIN-TOP:6PT;MARGIN-BOTTOM:0PT;TEXT-INDENT:4.86%;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN;FONT-SIZE:10PT;FONT-WEIGHT:NORMAL;FONT-STYLE:NORMAL;TEXT-TRANSFORM:NONE;FONT-VARIANT: NORMAL;">
	(ii) the information contained in the Report fairly presents, in all material respects, the financial condition and results of operations of the Company.
</P>
<P STYLE="MARGIN-TOP:2PT;MARGIN-BOTTOM:0PT;TEXT-INDENT:0%;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN;FONT-SIZE:10PT;FONT-WEIGHT:NORMAL;FONT-STYLE:NORMAL;TEXT-TRANSFORM:NONE;FONT-VARIANT: NORMAL;">

<EFX_CERTIFICATION>
<A NAME="FIS_CERTIFICATION_4"></A>
<P STYLE="TEXT-ALIGN:CENTER;MARGIN-TOP:12PT;MARGIN-BOTTOM:0PT;TEXT-INDENT:0%;FONT-WEIGHT:BOLD;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN;FONT-SIZE:10PT;FONT-STYLE:NORMAL;TEXT-TRANSFORM:NONE;FONT-VARIANT: NORMAL;">
	Certification of Chief Financial Officer
</P>
<P STYLE="TEXT-ALIGN:CENTER;MARGIN-BOTTOM:0PT;MARGIN-TOP:0PT;TEXT-INDENT:0%;FONT-WEIGHT:BOLD;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN;FONT-SIZE:10PT;FONT-STYLE:NORMAL;TEXT-TRANSFORM:NONE;FONT-VARIANT: NORMAL;">
	Pursuant to Section&#160;906 of the Sarbanes-Oxley Act of 2002
</P>
<P STYLE="MARGIN-TOP:12PT;MARGIN-BOTTOM:0PT;TEXT-INDENT:4.86%;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN;FONT-SIZE:10PT;FONT-WEIGHT:NORMAL;FONT-STYLE:NORMAL;TEXT-TRANSFORM:NONE;FONT-VARIANT: NORMAL;">
	Pursuant to 18 U.S.C. &#167;1350, as created by Section&#160;906 of the Sarbanes-Oxley Act of 2002, the undersigned officer of Mad Catz Interactive, Inc. (the &#8220;
<FONT STYLE="FONT-STYLE:ITALIC;">
	Company
</FONT>
	&#8221;) hereby certifies, to such officer&#8217;s knowledge, that:
</P>
<P STYLE="MARGIN-TOP:6PT;MARGIN-BOTTOM:0PT;TEXT-INDENT:4.86%;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN;FONT-SIZE:10PT;FONT-WEIGHT:NORMAL;FONT-STYLE:NORMAL;TEXT-TRANSFORM:NONE;FONT-VARIANT: NORMAL;">
	(i) the accompanying Annual Report on Form 10-K of the Company for the period ended March&#160;31, 2016 (the &#8220;
<FONT STYLE="FONT-STYLE:ITALIC;">
	Report
</FONT>
	&#8221;) fully complies with the requirements of Section&#160;13(a) or Section&#160;15(d), as applicable, of the Securities Exchange Act of 1934, as amended; and
</P>
<P STYLE="MARGIN-TOP:6PT;MARGIN-BOTTOM:0PT;TEXT-INDENT:4.86%;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN;FONT-SIZE:10PT;FONT-WEIGHT:NORMAL;FONT-STYLE:NORMAL;TEXT-TRANSFORM:NONE;FONT-VARIANT: NORMAL;">
	(ii) the information contained in the Report fairly presents, in all material respects, the financial condition and results of operations of the Company.
</P>
<P STYLE="MARGIN-BOTTOM:0PT;MARGIN-TOP:0PT;TEXT-INDENT:0%;FONT-FAMILY:TIMES NEW ROMAN;FONT-SIZE:10PT;FONT-WEIGHT:NORMAL;FONT-STYLE:NORMAL;TEXT-TRANSFORM:NONE;FONT-VARIANT: NORMAL;">
